`,n.jsx(r.p,{children:"In simple terms, AgentCore Runtime is a managed place to host agent or tool code. It handles concerns like session management, isolation, scaling, streaming, long-running work, protocol support, and observability so teams do not have to assemble all of that from scratch."}),`
